menuconfig ZMK_GATT_LAYER_EXPOSITION
    bool "Expose active layer over a custom GATT characteristic"
    depends on ZMK_BLE
    depends on !ZMK_SPLIT || ZMK_SPLIT_ROLE_CENTRAL
    default y
    help
      Exposes the highest active layer as a custom BLE GATT characteristic
      that supports read and notify operations for companion applications.
